IMAPAccount icloud
Host imap.mail.me.com
User gabrielgbrito@icloud.com
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only -d ~/etc/pass/icloud-mail.gpg"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore icloud-remote
Account icloud

MaildirStore icloud-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/icloud/
Inbox ~/mail/icloud/inbox

Channel icloud
Far :icloud-remote:
Near :icloud-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *

IMAPAccount dinf
Host mx.inf.ufpr.br
User ggb23
PassCmd "gpg -q --for-your-eyes-only -d ~/etc/pass/dinf.gpg"
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

IMAPStore dinf-remote
Account dinf

MaildirStore dinf-local
Subfolders Verbatim
Path ~/mail/dinf/
Inbox ~/mail/dinf/inbox

Channel dinf
Far :dinf-remote:
Near :dinf-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
